{"tid":1432236,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【連登公投】請問咁多位連登仔，你愛國愛港嘛？","createTime":"2019-08-08T07:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T07:55:58.000Z","uid":14328,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f84d40f2928a7f8f12a46fafbc9bc4aebfdce408","tid":1432236,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:45:35.000Z","msg":"每一場成功嘅社會運動，甚至係革命，「愛國主義」必然係處於社會中極盛嘅狀態。<br />\n因為「愛國」，賦予群眾極大正當性嘅動機。<br />\n<br />\n正如倪匡所說：「我唔愛國，我點解要反共？」<br />\n亦如年輕人所行，佢地唔愛港，點會大熱天時出嚟食催淚彈？<br />\n<br />\n當社會運動嘅抗爭之中，極大部分人嘅口號係：「愛國愛港」<br />\n愚蠢嘅愛國右膠，大腦會開始Hang機，覺得示威者係做得啱。<br />\n<br />\n中共／香港政府，一直極力聲稱香港人呢兩個月嘅運動，係叛亂，係暴動，係損害國家嘅行為。<br />\n<br />\n但如果呢個時候香港示威者正如歷史上所有煽動革命的成功者一樣：聲稱自己而家做緊嘅先係愛國行為，政府所做既先係反國家，唔愛國，所以人民要推翻呢個政府，將呢個國家重抬正軌。咁樣嘅話，會相當危險，因為往往「愛國」，係革命種子萌芽嘅開始。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔，你愛國愛港嘛？<br />\n<br />\n愛：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔愛：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee97eea01e22f7da3e07ef4dfe8eca90e6034d78","tid":1432236,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a17ee5ba687101077a270138aef015a5270a93","tid":1432236,"uid":55384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"愛港<br />\n國？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b7ff59c8e6226ca4fd13b2dfda33cd039b94d0","tid":1432236,"uid":27670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"愛國愛港不愛黨"},{"pid":"12e4e85ae54fdcc0d9a657777b3e2de1bbbfdeb4","tid":1432236,"uid":260529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:49:34.000Z","msg":"膠味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94182537ed03e16727f7efec05dfd94fc04b7da8","tid":1432236,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84a17ee5ba687101077a270138aef015a5270a93","tid":1432236,"uid":55384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"愛港<br />\n國？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:52:00.000Z","msg":"國家不代表共產黨<br />\n<br />\n要知道共產黨一直將「國家=共產黨」呢樣認知灌輸比人民<br />\n<br />\n而家好多人都覺得愛國=愛共產黨<br />\n<br />\n而家係要將呢樣野切割，你先可以團結到最多既人"},{"pid":"10d22bfe55cc705b39b3f62618f37521afeed69a","tid":1432236,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}